{"tid":1010496,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一個YouTube Playlist 聽到11個本地Indie Music 單位","createTime":"2019-02-06T04:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T02:39:14.000Z","uid":184592,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf5611964a89dd710d7990b274a896d16209955","tid":1010496,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.rthk.hk/assets/rthk/images/programme/dtt31/indiemusic/7508_programme_slider_20033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Frthk%2Fimages%2Fprogramme%2Fdtt31%2Findiemusic%2F7508_programme_slider_20033.jpg&h=46b289ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由香港電台製作，《硬地音樂/ Indie Music》介紹香港本地獨立樂隊或音樂人，2017年第一輯，而2018年第二輯嘅現出就喺下面：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c5gpO36O-Vs&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaIqrqgVtH5XB9fNPTPl6aum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc5gpO36O-Vs%26list%3DPLuwJy35eAVaIqrqgVtH5XB9fNPTPl6aum&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=89ee980b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c5gpO36O-Vs&amp;list=PLuwJy35eAVaIqrqgVtH5XB9fNPTPl6aum</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同場加映《硬地音樂》節目合集</strong></span><br />\n<strong>2017</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBPao4QvCv-EVGY1IUGKeCug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLKXvY9gpxoBPao4QvCv-EVGY1IUGKeCug&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=fdd5afde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBPao4QvCv-EVGY1IUGKeCug</a><br />\n觸執毛/ Tfvsjs/ 秋紅/ Sensi Lion/ 蔡世豪/ Interzone Collective/ Heyo/ 雞蛋蒸肉餅/ m.a.R.K./ ANWIYCTI<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2018</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBPMRJdrvHlG3hcY_7un2M2Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLKXvY9gpxoBPMRJdrvHlG3hcY_7un2M2Z&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=b8ae304c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBPMRJdrvHlG3hcY_7un2M2Z</a><br />\n鐵樹蘭/ Jason Kui/ Modern Children/ The Sulis Club、Adrian Lo/ Dough-Boy/ 粉紅A/ Instinct of Sight/ Thud/ Site Access/ Stranded Whale<br />\n<br />\n獨立樂隊或音樂人憑著對音樂的堅持與執著，選擇非主流路線，放棄商業機構作後盾。<br />\n硬地音樂絶對是一種態度。<br />\n每集節目會帶觀眾進入一個純音國度，分享本地獨立樂隊或音樂人的「真」音樂。<br />\n「硬地音樂」是獨立音樂的數碼舞台，讓觀眾接觸Cantopop以外的音樂。<br />\n節目亦會接觸獨立音樂界別的不同持分者，探討這音樂世界的生態。節目更取景於不同獨立音樂表演場地，讓觀眾更貼地接觸獨立音樂。"},{"pid":"1704826cca8b36c903ff2cc129018a23dfaf1ae2","tid":1010496,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"做乜又追住我嚟負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCanton pop又唔like<br />\nIndie又唔like<br />\n反本地嘢？"},{"pid":"4d4355dc30cc386e4003594c12ba67660c2a3090","tid":1010496,"uid":5739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"之前睇咗thud嗰個<br />\n覺得好正<br />\n跟埋佢地去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ff40edcbdc9c310ff58695e7a3b16e35958dab","tid":1010496,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d4355dc30cc386e4003594c12ba67660c2a3090","tid":1010496,"uid":5739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"之前睇咗thud嗰個<br />\n覺得好正<br />\n跟埋佢地去日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"我都有睇Thud嗰集，濛濛瀧瀧迷迷哋好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b42c28441eed99ac0c496cf0e470b9ab9905b6","tid":1010496,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"第一季我有開post嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c94a106204a65b5c9e67649e36588aab326ee4","tid":1010496,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike"